USAGE:

# Manual mode (creates prompts)
python3 scripts/orchestrator.py --source source/book.txt --book-name my-book --genre thriller

# Autonomous mode with Claude (high quality)
python3 scripts/orchestrator.py --source source/book.txt --book-name my-book --genre thriller --use-api --provider claude --max-budget 5.0

# Autonomous mode with DeepSeek (97% cost savings!)
python3 scripts/orchestrator.py --source source/book.txt --book-name my-book --genre thriller --use-api --provider deepseek --max-budget 1.0

# Compare provider costs
python3 scripts/llm_providers.py compare

COST EXAMPLES:
- DeepSeek: $0.05 per 80k-word book (CHEAPEST)
- Qwen: $0.10 per 80k-word book
- Claude: $1.85 per 80k-word book (HIGHEST QUALITY)
- OpenAI: $4.40 per 80k-word book

TIME: 2-4 hours for complete book (all providers)

RECOMMENDATION:
- Use DeepSeek for cost savings (97% cheaper than Claude)
- Use Claude for highest quality
- Test both with a single chapter first
